==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cranes-bill
<hw>Crane's"-bill`</hw> <pr>(kr?nz"b?l`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The geranium; -- so named from the long axis of
the fruit, which resembles the beak of a crane.</def> <rj><au>Dr.
Prior.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Surg.)</fld> <def>A pair of long-beaked
forceps.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Crang</ent>⟦br⟧
